    "x-status": "active",
    "x-team": "Equipe Education",
    "x-domain": "Education",
    "description": "Cours e-learning complets. Modules, vidéos, quiz et certification. DIFFERENCE vs training-api : Course = formation académique e-learning, Training = formation professionnelle en entreprise.",
